类分层结构

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.minecraft.world.BossInfo
      • net.minecraft.world.BossInfoServer
    • net.minecraft.world.ChunkCache (implements net.minecraft.world.IBlockAccess)
    • net.minecraft.world.ColorizerFoliage

    • net.minecraft.world.DifficultyInstance
    • net.minecraft.world.Explosion
    • net.minecraft.world.GameRules
    • net.minecraft.world.LockCode
    • net.minecraft.world.NextTickListEntry (implements java.lang.Comparable<T>)
    • net.minecraft.world.ServerWorldEventHandler (implements net.minecraft.world.IWorldEventListener)
    • net.minecraft.world.Teleporter (implements net.minecraftforge.common.util.ITeleporter)
    • java.lang.Throwable (implements java.io.Serializable)
      • java.lang.Exception
        • net.minecraft.world.MinecraftException
    • net.minecraft.util.math.Vec3i (implements java.lang.Comparable<T>)
      • net.minecraft.util.math.BlockPos
        • net.minecraft.world.Teleporter.PortalPosition
    • net.minecraft.world.World (implements net.minecraft.world.IBlockAccess, net.minecraftforge.common.capabilities.ICapabilityProvider)
      • net.minecraft.world.WorldServer (implements net.minecraft.util.IThreadListener)
        • net.minecraft.world.WorldServerDemo
        • net.minecraft.world.WorldServerMulti
    • net.minecraft.world.WorldEntitySpawner
    • net.minecraft.world.WorldProvider

      • net.minecraft.world.WorldProviderHell
      • net.minecraft.world.WorldProviderSurface
    • net.minecraft.world.WorldSettings
    • net.minecraft.world.WorldType
